# There once was an old man of Lyme
author: Edward Lear
source: Poetry Nook, *There once was an old man of Lyme*
sourceURL: https://www.poetrynook.com/poem/limerick-%E2%80%9Cthere-once-was-old-man-lyme%E2%80%9D

There was an old party of Lyme
Who married three wives at one time.
When asked:
	"Why the third?"
	He replied: "One's absurd,
And bigamy, sir, is a crime."
